scenes.description: Tokoyami Towa and Tsunomaki Watame perform 'Seishun Archive' on stage.
Transition animation showing the 'hololive production COUNTDOWN LIVE 2025▷2026' logo and progress graphics.
Usada Pekora, Shiranui Flare, Shirogane Noel, and Houshou Marine perform 'Yumemiru Sora e' on stage.

subtitles.original: 青春アーカイブ
subtitles.english: Seishun Archive

subtitles.original: イケる 素敵 頑張れ 落ちて
subtitles.english: You can do it, it's great, do your best, go for it

subtitles.original: 青春 感じていましょう 遊べ
subtitles.english: Let's feel our youth, let's play

subtitles.original: アッチュ！
subtitles.english: Atchu!

subtitles.original: 成長した姿を見せたい
subtitles.english: I want to show you how much I've grown

subtitles.original: ビバ 完璧 本番はもっと 全力で
subtitles.english: Viva! Perfect! In the real show, even more power!

subtitles.original: ハイ！ ハイ！ ホォー！
subtitles.english: Hi! Hi! Hoo!

subtitles.original: 大切な思い出
subtitles.english: Precious memories

subtitles.original: だってあるけどね まだ
subtitles.english: There are some, but still

subtitles.original: 感傷に浸ってる暇はない
subtitles.english: There's no time to soak in sentiment

subtitles.original: 今世紀最大の夏が始まる
subtitles.english: The biggest summer of the century is starting

subtitles.original: 想像の果てにある高み
subtitles.english: The heights at the end of imagination

subtitles.original: 勝ち取った景色は尊い
subtitles.english: The scenery we won is precious

subtitles.original: 逃げるな 限界の壁 越えて
subtitles.english: Don't run away, cross the wall of your limits

subtitles.original: 僕らはまだチャレンジャー Yeah!
subtitles.english: We are still challengers, yeah!

subtitles.original: 冷たい声に溺れたって
subtitles.english: Even if drowned out by cold voices

subtitles.original: 確かな爪をたぐり寄せるように
subtitles.english: As if reaching out to grab a foothold

subtitles.original: 期待外れだと誰かが嘆く
subtitles.english: Someone laments it's not what they expected

subtitles.original: 痛いと痛いがいつも戦う
subtitles.english: Pain and pain are always fighting

subtitles.original: プライドだけを頼りに抗う
subtitles.english: Resisting, relying only on pride

subtitles.original: 自分を信じたい
subtitles.english: I want to believe in myself

subtitles.original: 努力は報われる
subtitles.english: Effort will be rewarded

subtitles.original: 笑いたい奴は笑ってろ
subtitles.english: Let whoever wants to laugh, laugh

subtitles.original: 感傷に浸ってる暇はない
subtitles.english: There's no time to soak in sentiment

subtitles.original: 今世紀最大の夏が始まる
subtitles.english: The biggest summer of the century is starting

subtitles.original: 反響が足りない もっともっと
subtitles.english: The echo isn't enough, more, more

subtitles.original: 後悔はさせない
subtitles.english: I won't let you regret it

subtitles.original: 想像の果てにある高み
subtitles.english: The heights at the end of imagination

subtitles.original: 勝ち取った景色は尊い
subtitles.english: The scenery we won is precious

subtitles.original: 逃げるな 限界の壁 越えて
subtitles.english: Don't run away, cross the wall of your limits

subtitles.original: 僕らはまだチャレンジャー Yeah!
subtitles.english: We are still challengers, yeah!

subtitles.original: 夢見る空へ
subtitles.english: Yumemiru Sora e

subtitles.original: 重ねた手はぎゅっと離さずに
subtitles.english: Don't ever let go of our joined hands

subtitles.original: 行くよ 行こう 夢見る空へ
subtitles.english: Here we go, let's go, to the sky of our dreams

subtitles.original: 窓越しに見上げた
subtitles.english: Looking up through the window

subtitles.original: とても小さな空
subtitles.english: At a very small sky

subtitles.original: ここで出会えたのは
subtitles.english: Meeting here was

subtitles.original: 数えきれない奇跡
subtitles.english: A series of countless miracles

subtitles.original: 繰り返した一歩が
subtitles.english: The steps we repeatedly took

subtitles.original: きらめきをつないで
subtitles.english: Connected the sparkles

subtitles.original: 星のような笑顔
subtitles.english: A smile like a star

subtitles.original: 導いた
subtitles.english: Guided us

subtitles.original: Day by day みんなの声が力になる
subtitles.english: Day by day, everyone's voices become our strength

subtitles.original: Stage by stage ここでそれぞれ目指すもの
subtitles.english: Stage by stage, what we each aim for here

subtitles.original: それぞれ描くもの
subtitles.english: What we each portray

subtitles.original: それぞれ願った夢へ
subtitles.english: Towards the dreams we each wished for

subtitles.original: 重ねた手はぎゅっと離さずに
subtitles.english: Don't ever let go of our joined hands

subtitles.original: 一人ひとり違う色で描き出すときめき
subtitles.english: The excitement each of us paints in different colors

subtitles.original: 振り向くことなく真っ直ぐに
subtitles.english: Go straight ahead without looking back

subtitles.original: 行くよ 行こう 夢見る空へ
subtitles.english: Here we go, let's go, to the sky of our dreams

subtitles.original: 笑い合ったことや
subtitles.english: The times we laughed together

subtitles.original: 尽きない我が儘
subtitles.english: And our endless selfishness

subtitles.original: 思い出いっぱいなのに
subtitles.english: Even though there are so many memories
